搞間諜。你說病毒是從武漢傳出來的，我就說病毒是從美國傳來的。不需要有什麼證據，反正只要你說我什麼，我就反過來說你什麼。潑婦吵架經常用這一招，所以你不用把它看得太高深。外交部的發言就是這樣，講究的就是針鋒相對這四個字。你說我們怎麼樣，我們就要怎麼樣。你說我們不該怎麼做，我們就要怎麼做。我們全都列出來。"},{"pid":"b13db74b3f92904626a22647ae697745081c25f9","tid":2457111,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:44:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/60CfXJL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F60CfXJL.png&h=1c9fff17&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee6b0bb8b5335c763615d8345368fc69daabfc1e","tid":2457111,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:49:23.000Z","msg":"以為用法文出聲明添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"288b6aa7aec6cee266af6445499528acc992b7b0","tid":2457111,"uid":324280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T13:11:55.000Z","msg":"人地未戰狼喳 支那狗<br />\n真係戰狼起黎 支那狗跪低奶鞋底都奶唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3aa7b85381b5a2ebcccc2c04ec074327ccc9c56","tid":2457111,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T23:20:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5683865b282515edb5de2db27672e99ac7de56","tid":2457111,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T23:22:22.000Z","msg":"人地笑柒你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  真係以為自己戰狼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}